s=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>) → <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">h</span> : <span class=\"fn\">i</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#LT.lt\">&lt;</a> <span class=\"fn\">n</span>) → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> (<span class=\"fn\">i</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HAdd.hAdd\">+</a> <span class=\"fn\">1</span>) <span class=\"fn\">⋯</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span> <span class=\"fn\">⋯</span></span></span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">init</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">n</span> <span class=\"fn\">⋯</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">0</span> <span class=\"fn\">⋯</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Init/Data/Nat/Fold.lean#L230-L242","name":"Nat.dfold","line":230,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/Nat/Fold.html#Nat.dfold","doc":"`Nat.dfold` evaluates `f` on the numbers up to `n` exclusive, in increasing order:\n* `Nat.dfold f 3 init = init |> f 0 |> f 1 |> f 2`\nThe input and output types of `f` are indexed by the current index, i.e. `f : (i : Nat) → (h : i < n) → α i → α (i + 1)`.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/Nat/Fold.html#Nat.dfold\"><span class=\"name\">Nat</span>.<span class=\"name\">dfold</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\